column2:
For example, if using terminal:

curl --request POST \
  --url https://preview.api.climatiq.io/autopilot/v1-preview3/estimate \
  --header "Authorization: Bearer $CLIMATIQ_API_KEY" \
  --data '{
        "domain": "general",
        "text": "Steel",
        "parameters": {
                "money": 100,
        "money_unit": "usd"
        }
}'
